author: Xbox
description:
When you’re making a sequel, you can’t just repeat yourself. You must go bigger, stranger, and make even more questionably necessary swag. That’s why, to celebrate The Outer Worlds 2, we’re proud (and slightly bewildered) to introduce The Moon Man Couch-Panion — a 3 ft plush that’s equal parts collectible, cuddle buddy, and living room oddity.

Yes, you read that right. We made The Moon Man into a plush toy.

The Couch-Panion is no ordinary plush. This oversized lunar legend comes with stress-ball squishy hands (scientifically designed for rage-quitting), a popcorn bucket holder (for critical snack storage), and straps for your Xbox Wireless Controller and TV remote (because pockets are overrated). He doesn’t talk — thank goodness — but his oversized eyes practically scream: You are valid, even if I wouldn’t have made such a long lasting choice like you just did in the game.

Learn more on how you can win one of ten at Xbox Wire.
